<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <p>In the Kubernetes environment, Spaces reside in dedicated Data Pods that are completely separate from each other. Therefore, the same path can be used for each instance because each Space creates its own <code>persistentVolumeClaim</code>, and gets a separate <code>persistentVolume </code>from the <code>storageClass</code>.</p>
        <div class="tc-admon-note">
            <p>The defined path must be identical to the <code>volumeMount </code>path in the Data Pod.</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>